  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Tehwu un Mahtt fee pee\ntewis nizzina/ tan Sweschinee-\nkam darra tee Warras-Darbu\nfawa Widdû/ to Bahrixu un\nAtraitni tee eekſch tewim peewill.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Mannas ſivehtas Leetas\ntu nizzina/ un mannas Sweh-\nDeenas tu ſagahni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Pluſchketaij irr eekſch te-\nwim/ ka tee Affinis iſleti/ un tee\nehd eekſch tewim us Kalncem/ un\nturrahs negohdigi tawa Widdû.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Tee atſeds eekſch tewim\nta Tehwa Kaunumu/ un tahs\natschkirtas fahrnaizas ſceewas\ntee eekſch tewim atſihſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Ztts dsenn Negantibu ar\ntawa Tuwaka ſceewas/ zits ap-\ngahna negohdigi fawn Weddek-\ni/ atkaſ zits atſihſt fawn Mah-\nfu/ fawa Tehwa Meitu eekſch\ntewim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Tee nem eekſch tewim\nDahwanas/ Affinis iſleet / tee\ndsenn Angunu un plehſch Pa-\ngaidus/ ir tn eſti Negaufibu\ndſinnis pee tawa Tuwaka zaurn\nWarras- Darbu/ bet man-\nnis tu effi aiſmirſis/ fakka tas\nKungs KUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Rangi/ tad es faſittu\nmannas Diohkas tawas Negan-\nſibas deht/ ko tu dsenn/ un ta-\nwu Affinu pehz/ kas tawd Wid-\ndû irr iſleetas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Woj tawa Sirde pa-\nſtahwehs? buhs tad tawas Roh-\nas ſtipras tannis Deenâs/ kad\nes to ar tewim darrischu? Es tas\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "15. Un es iſkatſichu tewi\nstarp tein Bagaſeem/ un iſput-\ntinaschu tewi Wallês/ un iſuih-\nzinaschu no tewis tawu Neſchkik-\nſtibu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Ta tapſi tu ſagabnita\npreekſch to Bagaſu Azzim/ un\nſajuttifi/ ka es tas KUNgs eſmu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Atkat notifke ta KUNga\nWahrds us man/ un ſazzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Tu Zilweka Behrns/ tee\nno Israëka Namma irr man par\nSahrxeem tappuſchi/ tee wiſſi J\nirr Warsch jeb Alwa/ jeb Dſelse/\njeb Swins Zepta Widdû/ Sud-\nraba Sahrxi irr tee tappuſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Tadeht ta fakka tas\nKlings KUNGS: Tapehz ka\njuhs wiſſi effat par Sahrxeem\ntappuſchi/ tad redſi/ es ſapulzi-\nnaschu juhs widdu eekſch Jeru-\nsalemes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Itt ka Sudrabs/ jeb\nWarsch/jeb Dſelse/ jeb Swins/\njeb Alwa tohp kahdâ Zepta\nWiddû ſapulzinahts/ ka Ugguns\ntur appakſcha tohp uſpuhſts/ ka\ntas kanſehſs ktuhſt/ ta ſapulzi-\nnaschu es juhs eekſch mannas\nDuſmibas/ un atſahſchu juhs/\nun kanfeſchn juhs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "21. Teefcham/ es ſapulzinaschu\njuhs/ un uſpuhtischu prett jums\nto Ugguni mannas Duſmibas/\nka juhs tapſeet kanſetti winnas\nWiddû.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "22. Itt ka Sudrabs Zepli\ntohp kantehts / tapatt tapſeet\nMin\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
